15 It is hereby enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Vermont:
16 Sec. 1. FINDINGS
17 The General Assembly finds that:
18 (1) In 2023 and 2024, Vermont experienced extreme flooding and other
19 climate-fueled disasters that devastated farms and other working lands
20 businesses across the State.
