10 § 4632. FARM AND FORESTRY OPERATIONS SECURITY SPECIAL
11 FUND
12 (a) There is established the Farm and Forestry Operations Security Special
13 Fund to be administered by the Secretary of Agriculture, Food and Markets
14 and that shall be managed in accordance with 32 V.S.A. chapter 7, subchapter
15 5. The Fund shall consist of:
16 (1) funds appropriated by the General Assembly;
17 (2) funds from public and private sources that the Secretary accepts for
18 the Fund; and
19 (3) funds from federal government aid for State support of farmers
20 suffering income loss due to weather conditions.
