3 (4) Losses reimbursable by a grant under this section include:
4 (A) wages or compensation;
5 (B) replacement of lost income from destroyed crops, livestock, or
6 timber;
7 (C) debt payments or other ongoing expenses;
8 (D) costs of replanting;
9 (E) livestock feed replacement costs;
10 (F) infrastructure or equipment repair and replacement;
11 (G) repair of farm roads or logging roads; or
12 (H) other losses as determined by the Secretary after consultation
13 with the Review Board.
